==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὑγιής / hugiēs / hoog-ee-ace'

===Etymology===
*From the base of [[αὐξάνω]]; [[healthy]], that is, [[well]] (in body); figuratively [[true]] (in doctrine): 

===Adjective===
'''ὑγιής'''

#[[sound]], [[whole]].

